Microsoft Corp CEO Steve Ballmer To Retire Within 12 months
Friday, 23 Aug 2013 09:00am EDT
Microsoft Corp. announced that Chief Executive Officer (CEO) Steve Ballmer has decided to retire as CEO within the next 12 months, upon the completion of a process to choose his successor. In the meantime, Ballmer will continue as CEO and will lead Microsoft through the next steps of its transformation to a devices and services company.Â 
